alluxio.client.netty

Class NettyUnderFileSystemFileReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.client.netty.NettyUnderFileSystemFileReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UnderFileSystemFileReader, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    @NotThreadSafe
public final class NettyUnderFileSystemFileReader
extends Object
implements UnderFileSystemFileReader
    Reader for an under file system file through a worker's data server. This class does not hold any state specific to the file being read and can be used to read multiple files, but not concurrently. Close should be called on the reader if the caller no longer intends to use the reader in order to clean up any lingering data from the last read.
